[Episode 18]

15
00:01:09,180 --> 00:01:10,740
Ms. Bai has arrived.

16
00:01:42,980 --> 00:01:44,140
What is this about?

17
00:01:44,780 --> 00:01:47,020
The Bai family has invested
in the Qixiang Pavilion.

18
00:01:47,020 --> 00:01:49,260
The money we've spent can't go to waste.

19
00:01:49,420 --> 00:01:52,100
My husband has been managing
the pavilion for years.

20
00:01:52,100 --> 00:01:54,300
I do not know what tricks you used
to deceive Grandmother

21
00:01:54,300 --> 00:01:56,700
to the point she can't even tell
who is closer to the Ye family.

22
00:01:56,980 --> 00:01:58,900
Today, I will rid you

23
00:01:58,900 --> 00:02:00,220
on behalf of the Ye family.

24
00:02:24,540 --> 00:02:25,340
Buheng,

25
00:02:25,780 --> 00:02:28,660
I know you and Ye Buhan have had
a deep relationship over the years.

26
00:02:28,740 --> 00:02:29,860
But I'd like to ask you,

27
00:02:30,460 --> 00:02:31,700
over the years,

28
00:02:31,700 --> 00:02:33,260
who's been covering your meals

29
00:02:33,340 --> 00:02:34,900
and paying you your salary?

30
00:02:35,220 --> 00:02:38,140
You should know who your real master is.

31
00:02:43,660 --> 00:02:46,300
I only follow Mr. Ye for my entire life.

32
00:02:46,420 --> 00:02:47,340
Ms. Ying,

33
00:02:47,660 --> 00:02:49,940
I shall resign today.

34
00:02:50,340 --> 00:02:51,340
Take care.

35
00:02:54,180 --> 00:02:55,340
Yes, we're all quitting.

36
00:02:55,340 --> 00:02:55,980
Yes.

37
00:02:55,980 --> 00:02:57,020
The pavilion's not going to last.

38
00:02:57,020 --> 00:02:58,340
I, the purchasing manager,

39
00:02:58,340 --> 00:02:59,420
apply for resignation.

40
00:03:00,140 --> 00:03:01,180
I, the distribution manager,

41
00:03:01,180 --> 00:03:02,180
apply for resignation.

42
00:03:13,340 --> 00:03:14,340
Mr. Hao,

43
00:03:15,180 --> 00:03:19,100
I remember you're in charge
of ingredient purchases.

44
00:03:19,100 --> 00:03:21,380
