what your private accounts say.

52
00:03:44,100 --> 00:03:45,300
We can take this to the court

53
00:03:45,420 --> 00:03:46,820
with all the evidence.

54
00:03:46,820 --> 00:03:49,500
Falsifying accounts
and deceiving your employer

55
00:03:50,060 --> 00:03:51,660
is a crime that will send you to prison.

56
00:03:52,300 --> 00:03:54,340
Ms. Ying,

57
00:03:54,620 --> 00:03:56,340
