little by little.

68
00:04:15,500 --> 00:04:16,780
It has nothing to do with us.

69
00:04:16,980 --> 00:04:18,300
Please don't report it.

70
00:04:18,300 --> 00:04:19,140
Please don't.

71
00:04:19,140 --> 00:04:20,900
When did my brother do that?

72
00:04:20,900 --> 00:04:22,140
Don't slander us.

73
00:04:23,460 --> 00:04:26,580
There's no need
to continue with the rest.

74
00:04:26,900 --> 00:04:27,780
I'll just report it.

75
00:04:28,420 --> 00:04:29,140
Please don't.

76
00:04:29,140 --> 00:04:31,060
We were all misled by the Bai family.

77
00:04:31,060 --> 00:04:33,500
Please spare us, Ms. Ying.

78
00:04:33,500 --> 00:04:35,340
Please spare us.

79
00:04:41,020 --> 00:04:43,140
You've been with the pavilion
for quite some time.

80
00:04:43,540 --> 00:04:45,100
I can let you off,

81
00:04:45,820 --> 00:04:48,820
and what happened can stay in the past.

82
00:04:49,210 --> 00:04:50,090
[Ledger]

83
00:04:52,100 --> 00:04:54,100
Feel free to leave or stay.

84
00:04:54,100 --> 00:04:56,300
If you wish to stay,

85
00:04:56,300 --> 00:04:57,820
quit your corrupt thoughts.

86
00:04:58,260 --> 00:05:00,300
Work for your employer with honesty.

87
00:05:01,060 --> 00:05:02,740
Don't let me catch

88
00:05:02,860 --> 00:05:05,020
another violator.

89
00:05:05,020 --> 00:05:06,340
Thank you, Ms. Ying.

90
00:05:06,340 --> 00:05:08,100
We won't do it again.

91
00:05:08,100 --> 00:05:08,820
Thank you.

92
00:05:08,820 --> 00:05:11,340
You'd better hand over the management
as soon as possible.

93
00:05:11,340 --> 00:05:13,100
Grandmother decreed

94
00:05:13,100 --> 00:05:14,540
that the child I carry

95
00:05:14,540 --> 00:05:16,460
is Qixiang Pavilion's sole heir.

96
00:05:23,860 --> 00:05:26,260
You truly don't understand
incense, do you?

97
00:05:26,500 --> 00:05:27,740
If you were pregnant,

98
00:05:28,540 --> 00:05:31,780
