in a pitiful situation.

102
00:05:44,460 --> 00:05:46,060
You may sign this divorce agreement.

103
00:05:46,660 --> 00:05:47,620
After you sign,

104
00:05:48,100 --> 00:05:49,660
you'll be free

105
00:05:50,140 --> 00:05:51,380
and can marry whoever you wish.

106
00:05:51,740 --> 00:05:53,120
